config:
  theme: neo-dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant RN as React Native App
    participant API as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User ->> RN: Enter username & password
    RN ->> API: POST /auth/login
    API ->> DB: SELECT user WHERE username
    DB -->> API: User record + password hash
    API ->> API: Verify password (bcrypt compare)
    API -->> RN: JWT token + user object
    RN -->> User: Redirect to Home


---
config:
  theme: neo-dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant RN as React Native App
    participant API as Backend
    participant CF as Google Cloud Function
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User ->> RN: Capture passport image
    RN ->> API: POST /verify/passport (multipart)
    API ->> CF: Forward image (no local storage)
    CF ->> CF: Google Cloud Vision OCR
    CF ->> CF: Extract and filter MRZ lines
    CF -->> API: MRZ lines
    API ->> API: Parse and validate MRZ checksums
    API ->> API: HMAC-SHA256(documentNumber|country|expiry, SALT)
    API ->> DB: INSERT verifications (type=passport, level=2, passport_hash)
    DB -->> API: Constraint check - unique active passport hash
    API ->> DB: UPDATE users SET verification_tier = GREATEST(tier, 2)
    API -->> RN: Success - level 2 granted
    RN -->> User: Passport verified


---
config:
  theme: neo-dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant RN as React Native App
    participant API as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User ->> RN: Swipe to vote on poll
    RN ->> API: POST /polls/vote (JWT + pollId + choice)
    API ->> API: Validate JWT - extract userId
    API ->> DB: Query verifications WHERE user_id AND not revoked AND not expired
    DB -->> API: effectiveTier + passportHash
    API ->> DB: SELECT required_verification_tier FROM poll_groups
    DB -->> API: Required tier
    API ->> API: Check effectiveTier >= requiredTier
    API ->> DB: INSERT poll_identity_usage (poll_id, passport_hash)
    DB -->> API: Unique constraint - reject if duplicate
    API ->> API: generateActionToken - crypto.randomBytes(32)
    API ->> DB: INSERT action_tokens (token_hash, poll_vote, poll_id)
    API ->> DB: INSERT poll_votes (poll_id, token_hash, choice)
    API ->> DB: INSERT poll_participation (user_id, poll_id) UI only
    API ->> DB: COMMIT transaction
    API -->> RN: Success
    RN -->> User: Vote recorded





